name: PatroMedic Blood Bank
description: Every day, roughly 36,000 units of red blood cells are needed in the World. Patients with sickle cell diseases or cancer need blood transfusions throughout their treatments, and a single car accident victim can require up to 100 pints of blood.

name: Emergency Health Support
description: All around the world, acutely ill and injured people seek care every day.  Frontline providers manage children and adults with medical, surgical and obstetric emergencies, including injuries and infections.

name: Cardiothoracic Surgery
